<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Cudgel2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Cudgel,</orth> vb. to beat with a stick: <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.5.99" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. IV, 5, 99</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 5.4.115" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado V, 4, 115</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 2.5.145" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. II, 5, 145</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 2.464" default="NO" valid="yes">John II, 464</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 5.2.138" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 138</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.3.100" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 3, 100</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.3.100" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 3, 100</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.3.100" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 3, 100</bibl> <bibl n="shak. h5 5.1.90" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 V, 1, 90</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 3.3.249" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. III, 3, 249</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 2.3.372" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. II, 3, 372</bibl>. <cit><quote>c. thy brains no more about it,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 5.1.63" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. V, 1, 63</bibl></cit> (the clown's speech; cf. <emph>Beat</emph>).
